{"tid":255013,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]豹貓係英國移民返香港 證書有問題","createTime":"2017-05-23T15:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T20:08:29.000Z","uid":98121,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"851caeaf3b3a51b7740a1c0fc0d2a7b8fb78eea5","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯左係吹水台，所以開多次喺度，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的<br />\n我同男朋友2年前係英國透過breeder買咗隻豹貓返嚟<br />\n嗰陣時第一日去breeder屋企本來好多野都好正常<br />\n臨走時先俾張證書我哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時都覺得張證書流流地<br />\n但係都諗住返屋企search下真嘅係點先攞嚟同佢對質，反正有佢屋企地址同電話<br />\n<br />\n點知返到屋企幾個鐘之後<br />\n發現原來隻貓係病病地<br />\n即刻帶佢去睇醫生<br />\n醫生話佢呢啲病冇可能係幾個鐘頭得返嚟，一定最起碼幾日之前<br />\n我哋即刻打電話同send message去breeder度問佢發生咩事<br />\n然後佢電話唔聽，屋企冇人開門，只係過幾日覆message話要去第二國家探爺爺<br />\n從嗰日開始就冇辦法再聯絡到佢<br />\n加上男朋友之前壞電話<br />\n所有breeder record 都冇晒<br />\n<br />\n依家搞緊搵運隻貓返香港啲嘢<br />\n美國嗰邊話一定要official證書證明佢係第五代<br />\n但我哋根本搵唔番個breeder<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有經驗可以幫下我地<br />\n我真係好想運佢返香港<br />\n佢每日都陪我瞓覺叫我起身<br />\n仲要超級嗲<br />\n係我最唔開心同得我一個人嘅時候陪住我<br />\n求求大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩手法都請大家話俾我知，呢度唔方便講，tg都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg:Lihkgkaka"},{"pid":"9fa0c1172ffc4daf4aaf8c7b2246273cec0bc1e6","tid":255013,"uid":51388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"整做標本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43bc0643b5eec0bb9ba64c6842f0b972a3590a8","tid":255013,"uid":107605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇過你開錯台個post<br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e3b10067a80fcbd97d57db45e38388c07fe136","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整做標本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b491825ad1a9725643523a6232c2b1a4936e42","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱睇過你開錯台個post<br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890816b62497fd0bb6d115cc29084164c8a3d566","tid":255013,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5813b6dd794b5b6d3407caa823a7a6a47b10696e","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Push</blockquote><br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d594ce221da8267b298174c48afcf75834fb3c","tid":255013,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T17