msg":"影兩張相放生啦<br />\n人類唔好咁自私啦"},{"pid":"2745cf240fc12e82a456ce663451113f9511b8b1","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T21:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影兩張相放生啦<br />\n人類唔好咁自私啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時開露台道門<br />\n出面成個草地佢都唔會出去<br />\n就算格硬抱佢出去散步<br />\n佢都會即刻跑番入屋"},{"pid":"49c1143b58c5089fcd1cf65298ec4a9662cdf4b7","tid":255013,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T21:55:01.000Z","msg":"番香港托柒咩"},{"pid":"527347d051fc1a2633606ed6438e7822ba89666e","tid":255013,"uid":24364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:29:56.000Z","msg":"番黎既時候死話係街貓得唔得？反正海關都無證據話佢係豹貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"e826472ca1185b4879cba2de12e042c3dcf98cd8","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番黎既時候死話係街貓得唔得？反正海關都無證據話佢係豹貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up</blockquote><br />\n有位絲打話如果無晶片的話<br />\n可以係打晶片時<br />\n同獸醫講佢係Mix breed<br />\n但係可惜我一早已經幫佢即值咗晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064116d7144b205b35ea62a40462627c7ded090b","tid":255013,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"非法入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c76c1219cd0b985b5057d37195999a202253da","tid":255013,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"Bengal cat?🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇🍇"},{"pid":"d11f72a0474234239be39ebfc1f065c3c96177e0","tid":255013,"uid":98121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非法入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla